  The star stunned her 41.8 million Instagram followers in the red-hot ensemble, which featured a plunging mesh neckline and see-through section in the skirt. She paired the long-sleeved garment with one of her favourite silver necklaces and wore her voluminous tresses parted on the side. Britney posed in a pair of sky-high brown stiletto heels, effortlessly pivoting as she moved rhythmically to the beat of a song. “Red,” she captioned the video that saw her flaunting her figure in different parts of her home.   